0 fully buffed a couple nights ago..I was giddy as hell. <img src=icon_smile.gif border=0 align=middle></P><P>My goal is 2.5khp at 60 unbuffed. My dream goal is 3.5khp unbuffed.</P><P>And why AA grind at 54? /shrug to each their own I guess, but I'll wait till 60 first. Or at least 59. </P><P>A fast recap- more hp=increased surviveability if shit hits the fan. I take alot of risks. I find them enjoyable. I find myself taking many many hits. HP>* for me after 200int. If you get by just fine with lower HP due to YOUR playstyle, then good for you. Don't worry about why I think HP is more important then. You've already made up your mind that it's not important for you anyways. /shrug, why'd this topic even come up again?</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=264137" target="_blank" target="_blank">Charbonez Soulmark</a><BR>Clan Doomit<BR>Duzzil Ro</font></td>
